   Blythe: Is this like TOMS, where if I eat a Jim Shoe, someone in Africa
   gets mailed a Jim Shoe?

   Ian: You can also get a James Shoe, which is the same thing but you eat
   it with the proper fork.

   Miles: It seems strange at first, but I get significantly fewer stares
   wearing these to the gym rather than my Vibram Five Fingers.
   The Jim Shoe is so good, Ian doesn't care that he's very likely about
   to be kidnapped by van people. [35]Enlarge image [36]i

